title: Scott Bairstow #Bair#
description:
A working actor frimageom the age of ten, Bair also found his passion in music. Both his parents are classical musicians and many influences come from their support. The old 70s and folk sounds are a passion of Bair's and so he chose to follow that path for music. People who have heard his CD have described it as heartfelt, emotional, truth revealing.
